 apply o</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-style:normal">n a UK wide basis</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-style:normal">. Last </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-style:normal">year, the success rate of appeals was 39% industry wide, and 30% in the case of Barclays. While these successful appeals are often a result of new information</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-style:normal"> being provided by the customer</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-style:normal">, </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-style:normal">we</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-style:normal"> </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-style:normal">have</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-style:normal"> focussed on creating as effective a decision making proce</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-style:normal">ss as possible for the initial application.</span></li><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 10.06pt; padding-left:7.94pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-style:normal">At the heart of this process is a ‘one for yes, two for no’ mechanism where any application declined in the initial assessment is subject to further consideration from another colleague.</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-style:normal"> </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-style:normal">We aim to ensure that we</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-style: