 meeting their needs.</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-style:normal">  </span></li><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 10.06pt; padding-left:7.94pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-style:normal">In the case of</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-style:normal"> Barclays, we remain committed to enhancing access to finance, through a thorough initial application process, an effective system of appeals, and by encouraging businesses to consider the wide range of funding sources available to them.</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-style:normal"> </span></li><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt 10.06pt; padding-left:7.94pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-style:normal">This process is a</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-style:normal">pplied consistently on a UK basis, including Northern Ireland.</span></li></ul><p style="font-size:11pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold">Conclusion</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-style:normal">Barclays has continued to invest and expand its business in Northern Ireland throughout the recession.</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-style:normal"> </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-style:normal">We offer a full service to our customers in Northern Ireland, who are at no d</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-style:normal">isadvant